pr_title: FINERACT-1006 Added spotless to auto format source code
pr_body:
FINERACT-1006

@vorburger  fineractdev-eclipse-preferences.epf, the file that you provided, was not suitable to be used as config. I imported and exported the same as XML(there is a guide on spotless on how to do it https://github.com/diffplug/spotless/blob/master/ECLIPSE_SCREENSHOTS.md ).

The following works great:
For testing, you can use ./gradlew spotlessJavaCheck to run the checks and ./gradlew spotlessApply to fix violations. 

The problem now? 
I don't think fineractdev-eclipse-preferences.xml that we currently use is in the correct format as required by us, it adds trailing spaces after we run ./gradlew spotlessApply at some specific points.

Rest this is a really good improvement :) 
#933
